summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting electrical underground and surface rights distribution easements over portions of Government Lot 2, Section 10, Township 24 North, Range 4 East, W.M.; Lot 11, Block 8, Westwood Park; Parcels B, C and D, all in City of Seattle Short Subdivision 9000526; Block 12 of Chittenden's Terrace Park; Lot 26, Block 5, McKenzie and Dempsey's Lake Washington Addition; the vacated alley in Block M, Bell's 5th Addition; Lot 1, Block 25, Innis Arden Division No. 3; Lot 11, Block 1 Cedar Park No. 3; and placing said easements under the jurisdiction of the City Light Department.
